  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. All seven assessed credibility factors are evaluated against MRL-5 requirements; the six remaining factors are flagged as epistemic gaps. Decision: Accepted based on documented factor outcomes and UQ envelope.",
  "currentModelVersion": "ansys-cfx-2026-q1-build-7",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-absolute",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-below-threshold",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-centrifugal-pump-cfd-hemolysis",
