      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) below 5% for HI QoI on at least three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study performed (0.9M, 2.1M, 4.2M elements). GCI for velocity magnitude 3.2%; GCI for hemolysis index 7.8%, exceeding the 5% target. Discretization error is the primary gap between achieved and required level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
