      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (e.g., E_rms) computed with uncertainty bounds on both simulation and experiment; statistical comparison required.",
      "rationale": "Mean absolute error and max error reported across 5 operating points. Experimental measurement uncertainty (±6%) and simulation UQ interval (Monte Carlo, 95th percentile) both reported. Formal hypothesis test against equivalence threshold not performed; limits achieved level to 3."
    },
