      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry used for validation is a recognized benchmark but differs from the proprietary VAD impeller geometry in blade sweep angle and volute design. Flow regime (Re, Womersley) is representative. Geometry gap limits relevance to achieved level 3."
